> I don't think there is a problem here. You should only use arrow functions if you understand how they work: they capture lexical `this`.

箭头函数是捕获定义时外层作用域，我这样写，methods[key]还没有被定义。当点击事件触发的时候才定义methods[key]（我们组件内部写的箭头函数），然后此时外层作用域被我们绑定到了vm上，箭头函数自然就是vm实例。并且我做过测试，这样写组件内部的箭头函数是可以拿到vm实例的。普通函数和箭头函数都可以拿到vm实例
function changethis() {
  return () => methods[key].call(this)
}

```javascript
// PatchChild.vue
<template>
  <div>
    {{ data.key }}
  </div>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: {
    data: {
      type: Object,
      required: true,
    },
  },
};
</script>
``` 


```javascript
// Wrapper.vue
<template>
  <div>
    <div>
      <PatchChild v-for="item in list" :key="item.key" :data="item" />
    </div>
    <div><button @click="changeList">changeList</button></div>
  </div>
</template>

<script>
import PatchChild from './PatchChild.vue';

export default {
  components: {
    PatchChild,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      list: [
        {
          key: 'A',
        },
        {
          key: 'B',
        },
        {
          key: 'C',
        },
      ],
    };
  },
  methods: {
    changeList() {
      this.list = [
        {
          key: 'D',
        },
        {
          key: 'B',
        },
        {
          key: 'B',
        },
        {
          key: 'E',
        },
      ];
    },
  },
};
</script>
```
